Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:18.04,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勿忘懷  此相思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:28.74,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信  愛之共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:37.96,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}擁夜入眠  殘月鳴泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:43.87,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}罪劫輪回  惑月迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:50.03,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}滿盈圓缺  無痕冰消
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:56.63,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}千千心結  若縛君影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.99,0:23:03.01,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}則至神允  墜天之志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:07.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}深信此愛  永不相棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:14.57,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}細語聲中憶往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:20.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛恨交結暗之樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:27.13,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此相思  永相連
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:37.82,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}入我夢  時之歌
